            <h2 class="section-heading font-bold text-white mb-6">
              Weekly Accountability<br />Built for Engagement
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
              Our accountability system keeps your community motivated through
              friendly competition and social accountability. Set weekly goals, track
              progress, and celebrate wins together.
